This file is to test host name insted of ip address
while sending file from one server to another server.
to do this below is the procedure.
hostname -i ===> we will get one hostcode, this we have to add in the another server as mentioned below
/etc/hosts ===> in this file we have to add the other server host id and need to give alias name like 11:11:11:11  tomcat

same procedure we have to do in the another server also.

after this we can send the file to another server like below

scp -r <file> tomcat:<path>
